{"tid":1405193,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"FGO 最新英靈: 香港的Archer","createTime":"2019-08-04T08:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T12:04:49.000Z","uid":51185,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62e1f4f59cb6425185b5c62320ba8f7e91683724","tid":1405193,"uid":51185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"FGO 最新英靈: 香港的Archer<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/f4xBTBS/hkarcher.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Ff4xBTBS%2Fhkarcher.png&h=b5d6b0fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n職階技能:<br />\n陣地建造：A+<br />\n道具作成：A+<br />\n氣息遮斷：B<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n紅卡寶具: 流星一條 (Stella)<br />\n對敵方全體發動超強大的攻擊(Over Charge時威力提升)+自身HP-99999。(可被技三毅力狀態救回)<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n持有技能:<br />\n技一: 香港人加油<br />\n全體紅魔放一回合(lv10)，獲得爆擊星(lv10)(CD 6)<br />\n<br />\n技二: 對抗黑警惡勢力<br />\n對惡及獸屬性加成(lv10)三回合(CD 5)<br />\n<br />\n技三: 不受傷，不被捕，不割蓆，齊上齊落<br />\n賦予自身迥避狀態(1回合)，賦予毅力狀態(lv10)(1次, 三回合) (CD 7)"},{"pid":"7fc62052c4511031aaee7e6aa3c68d86f285b37f","tid":1405193,"uid":247554,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VXOxp6U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVXOxp6U.png&h=14d182a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港的sheilder <br />\n<br />\n以下開放創作"},{"pid":"6a5611228e823774c87f47ed5489c86696057c6f","tid":1405193,"uid":51185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb9695e58aa13c9adeeec531cdd9674721f7511","tid":1405193,"uid":650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:28:38.000Z","msg":"點解係全體唔係單體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c60ab3fa4fca20a49